OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FA group of MPs has called for a raft
OL,8,Fof measures aimed at tackling rising
OL,9,Frates of skin cancer, including
OL,10,Fcigarette-style warnings on sunbeds
OL,11,Fand cheaper sunscreen.
OL,13,FThe All-Party Parliamentary Group for
OL,14,FBeauty, Hair & Wellbeing said
OL,15,Foverexposure to ultraviolet (UV)
OL,16,Fradiation from both natural and
OL,17,Fartificial sources represents a
OL,18,Fsevere, yet entirely preventable,
OL,19,Fpublic health crisis in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FAccording to Cancer Research UK,
OL,8,Faround seven people die from melanoma
OL,9,Feach day in the UK.
OL,11,FMelanoma is the most severe form of
OL,12,Fskin cancer, and cases are expected to
OL,13,Fincrease by almost 10% by 2040.
OL,15,FWhat are the symptoms of melanoma?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FThe main cause of melanoma is exposure
OL,8,Fto ultraviolet light from the sun or
OL,9,Fsunbeds. Symptoms can include a new
OL,10,Fmole or a change in an existing mole,
OL,11,Fespecially variations in shape,
OL,12,Fborder, colour or size over time.
OL,14,FWhy are changes needed?
OL,16,FThe MPs said: "Despite UV radiation
OL,17,Fbeing officially classified by the
OL,18,FWorld Health Organisation as a Group 1
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,Fcarcinogen, the UK currently lacks a
OL,8,Fcohesive, national strategy to
OL,9,Fmitigate its impact, leaving the
OL,10,Fpopulation hugely vulnerable to a
OL,11,Fthreat that will only escalate with
OL,12,Fclimate change."
OL,14,FWhat are their recommendations?
OL,16,FThey said there was no single fix for
OL,17,Fthe issue, but called for a range of
OL,18,Fchanges to help mitigate rates of skin
OL,19,Fcancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FAmong their recommendations was
OL,8,Fscrapping VAT on children's sunscreen
OL,9,Fand reducing it to 5% on adult
OL,10,Fsunscreen.
OL,12,FThey said sunscreen should be
OL,13,Freclassified as "preventative
OL,14,Fhealthcare" rather than a luxury
OL,15,Fcosmetic.
OL,17,FThey also called for sunbeds to be put
OL,18,Funder similar regulation to
OL,19,Fcigarettes, saying advertisements
OL,20,Fshould be banned and health warnings
OL,21,Fpresented to customers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FMPs highlighted a study published in
OL,8,Fthe British Medical Journal, which
OL,9,Ffound that using sunbeds before age 35
OL,10,Fincreases melanoma risk by 59%.
OL,12,FAnother recommendation was to classify
OL,13,FUV radiation as an occupational
OL,14,Fhazard, forcing businesses to provide
OL,15,Fappropriate protection to employees
OL,16,Fwho work mostly outdoors.
OL,18,FMPs said research they had seen
OL,19,Fsuggested outdoor workers face a 60%
OL,20,Fhigher risk of non-melanoma skin
OL,21,Fcancer compared to indoor workers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FThey also encouraged better education
OL,8,Fand communication around the issue to
OL,9,Fcombat misinformation.
OL,11,FHow will it be funded?
OL,13,FMPs said the loss in VAT revenue would
OL,14,Fbe made up by reducing the estimated
OL,15,Fannual cost to the NHS for treating
OL,16,Fskin cancer, which is around #750
OL,17,Fmillion.
OL,19,FDo the proposals face opposition?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
