PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FIn response to the findings, Gary
OL,8,FLipman, chairman of the Sunbed
OL,9,FAssociation (TSA), the representative
OL,10,Fbody for professional tanning salons
OL,11,Fthroughout the UK and Ireland, told
OL,12,FITV News: "The UK already has strict
OL,13,Flegislation governing commercial
OL,14,Fsunbeds, including a ban on under-18
OL,15,Fuse, supervision requirements, and
OL,16,Flimits on UV output."
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
