OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,FThe real problem is inconsistent
OL,8,Fenforcement against a minority of
OL,9,Frogue operators, not professional
OL,10,Fsalons that follow the rules, he said.
OL,12,F"Adults should be free to make
OL,13,Finformed choices within a properly
OL,14,Fregulated environment, and our polling
OL,15,Fshows the public overwhelmingly
OL,16,Fsupports regulation and enforcement
OL,17,Frather than prohibition.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1778702756
OL,3,CCould cigarette-style warnings on
OL,4,Csunbeds and cheaper SPFs fight skin
OL,5,Ccancer?
OL,7,F"We are concerned by attempts to
OL,8,Fcompare regulated sunbed use with
OL,9,Ftobacco, which are neither
OL,10,Fproportionate nor reflective of the
OL,11,Fevidence discussed during the inquiry.
OL,13,F"The focus should be on standards,
OL,14,Fenforcement, and consumer safety, not
OL,15,Fheadline-grabbing comparisons that
OL,16,Frisk driving people towards
OL,17,Funregulated environments."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@ZO]
